            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "萬國數據私人配售3億美元換股價予華泰  息3.75%行使價溢價17.5%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">萬國數據(09698)宣佈私人配售3億美元B輪可轉換優先股予中國機構投資者華泰資本。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"萬國數據官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/09698.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"萬國數據官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/09698.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">萬國數據官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">款項將動用私人配售所得款項擴充數據中心容量及作一般企業用途。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">可轉換優先股發行日期起的首6年，每年累計至少3.75%的股息。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">持有人選擇轉換為萬國數據的A類普通股，轉換率對應的轉換價約為每股GDS美國存託股54.43美元，2026年1月30日香港收市價溢價約17.5%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">可轉換優先股若悉數行使，將會發行合共約551.2萬股美國存託股，或4409.66萬股普通股，佔公告日期公司發行股份總額2.62%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15627971-%e8%90%ac%e5%9c%8b%e6%95%b8%e6%93%9a%e7%a7%81%e4%ba%ba%e9%85%8d%e5%94%ae3%e5%84%84%e7%be%8e%e5%85%83%e6%8f%9b%e8%82%a1%e5%83%b9%e4%ba%88%e8%8f%af%e6%b3%b0-%e6%81%af3-75%e8%a1%8c%e4%bd%bf%e5%83%b9",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/09698-2024.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-31 16:48:18",
